---
title: Herby Asparagus and Tomato Bake with Israeli Couscous, Oregano and Feta
description: Feta cheese is delicious on its own, but marinated feta is a whole new level of tasty. Roasted asparagus and tomatoes pair beautifully with Israeli couscous mixed with a tangy balsamic dressing. The marinated feta is the crown on this royally tasty dish.
